10.25.20  8:58 am   Do you have an ETA on your next video and not telling anyone or do you just have no idea when or when. Or when you get your software working do u have an ETA after the software is working?

      i had one, which is in the past. usually when you miss a date, it is almost impossible to make another date. i am grappling with the immense greed of my creative mind, and the complete inability to set any kind of boundaries. this has plagued me for my entire life and it is my number 1 enemy. but, as always, i will find my way through, because i am overflowing with new songs and ideas, as usual
